{"TopicId":173650,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Can you recommend my good aviation (flight) simulator where i can declare MAYDAY MAYDAY MAYDAY via ATC :-)","CreatedByName":"Pawelk198604","CreatedById":35539,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-08T18:40:18Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Pawelk198604","CreatedById":35539,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-08T18:40:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have Flight Sim World, MFS X, and tried X Plane but returned to steam\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFlight Simulator have only VFR flight MFSX is good but old, and i nether simulator we can declare\u00A0MAYDAY\u00A0MAYDAY\u00A0MAYDAY\u00A0 even if we had total engine failure \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/SDEdlB0xGfU?start=25\u0026amp;feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022459\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nibb31","CreatedById":7272,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-08T19:59:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPilots never say MAYDAY MAYDAY MAYDAY over the radio.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pawelk198604","CreatedById":35539,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-08T21:58:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223349150\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173650\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221523217546\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u00227272\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nibb31\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Nibb31 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPilots never say MAYDAY MAYDAY MAYDAY over the radio.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DAL59","CreatedById":180784,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-09T02:03:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFSX is a multiplayer realistic flight sim with voice chat\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-04-09T02:04:32Z\u0022 title=\u002204/09/2018 02:04  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EApril 9, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by DAL59\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-09T04:44:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223349396\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173650\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221523239437\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022180784\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DAL59\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, DAL59 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFSX... realistic...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHa. ha. ha.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/hfhK37dCfPg?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022459\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"munlander1","CreatedById":168560,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-09T06:19:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223349150\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173650\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221523217546\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u00227272\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nibb31\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, Nibb31 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPilots never say MAYDAY MAYDAY MAYDAY over the radio.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat do they say?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-09T06:40:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223349495\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173650\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221523254758\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022168560\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022munlander1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n40 minutes ago, munlander1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat do they say?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022... Declaring emergency\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe only time they\u0027d call \u0022mayday\u0022 \u003Cs\u003Eis when death is seconds away.\u003C/s\u003E Another is \u0022pan\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT :\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlright, it seems things are slightly more than what I thought.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://code7700.com/emergency.htm\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://code7700.com/emergency.htm\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is true that if you only have the slightest of problems such declaration might not be really necessary; on the other hand, I\u0027m reminded of what happens when you don\u0027t properly call out to others\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indonesia_AirAsia_Flight_8501\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ewhen wrong things are happening\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo yeah, these words are actually a very powerful tool. It\u0027s like that \u0022abort\u0022 button on your rocket in KSP (or real life TBH).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut as one infamous quote says : \u003Cem\u003E\u0022With great power, comes great responsibility\u0022\u003C/em\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-04-09T07:01:12Z\u0022 title=\u002204/09/2018 07:01  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EApril 9, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by YNM\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nibb31","CreatedById":7272,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-09T07:51:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223349495\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173650\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221523254758\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022168560\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022munlander1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, munlander1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat do they say?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe 3 rules for a pilot are:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nAviate: Keep the plane flying (or landing).\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nNavigate: Know where you are, figure out where you\u0027re going.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nCommunicate: First with your co-pilot and crew.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nNote that Communicate comes last, and even then, the priority is to communicate with those who are able to actually help you Aviate and Navigate.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn an emergency, a pilot should concentrate on the flying. You only communicate when you have the plane under control and you know where you are.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnce you have time to actually Communicate, the last thing you want to do is to scream \u0022MAYDAY\u0022 over the radio. That serves absolutely zero purpose. It\u0027s much more useful to calmly state your emergency, your cockpit readings, and your position.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-04-09T07:52:45Z\u0022 title=\u002204/09/2018 07:52  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EApril 9, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Nibb31\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-09T08:01:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223349533\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173650\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221523260308\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u00227272\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nibb31\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, Nibb31 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat serves absolutely zero purpose.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you\u0027re out of fuel somewhere low and far, maybe. If you\u0027re out of fuel high and close, might be a good one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLook up this accident. Aviate, sure, but to no avail.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indonesia_AirAsia_Flight_8501\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indonesia_AirAsia_Flight_8501\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould have been better if they had communicated the anomalies out and down.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-04-09T08:05:11Z\u0022 title=\u002204/09/2018 08:05  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EApril 9, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by YNM\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nibb31","CreatedById":7272,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-09T09:20:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223349536\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173650\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221523260888\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298447\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022YNM\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, YNM said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you\u0027re out of fuel somewhere low and far, maybe. If you\u0027re out of fuel high and close, might be a good one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLook up this accident. Aviate, sure, but to no avail.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indonesia_AirAsia_Flight_8501\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indonesia_AirAsia_Flight_8501\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks like that accident was mostly due to not aviating (the co-pilot disconnecting a vital system and not realizing the consequences) and then miscommunication between the crew. Yelling \u0022MAYDAY\u0022 over the radio would have served no purpose.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, YNM said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould have been better if they had communicated the anomalies out and down.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs opposed to yelling \u0022MAYDAY\u0022, which was my point. No distress signal was sent, because the crew was probably busy trying to recover from the stall.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-09T09:27:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223349569\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173650\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221523265624\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u00227272\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nibb31\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Nibb31 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks like that accident was mostly due to not aviating\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGiven the loose soldering, it\u0027s questionable if at the time it really was airworthy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"p1t1o","CreatedById":74091,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-09T10:32:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223349150\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173650\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221523217546\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u00227272\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nibb31\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, Nibb31 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPilots never say MAYDAY MAYDAY MAYDAY over the radio.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey might\u00A0not, but there is official voice procedure in various countries which describes how and when a mayday\u00A0call should be made.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-04-09T10:32:18Z\u0022 title=\u002204/09/2018 10:32  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EApril 9, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by p1t1o\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-04-09T10:49:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223349586\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022173650\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221523269928\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274091\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022p1t1o\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n24 minutes ago, p1t1o said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthere is official voice procedure in various countries\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nActually, it\u0027s by ICAO. (or FAA in the US.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://flightservicebureau.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/ICAO-Doc4444-Pans-Atm-16thEdition-2016-OPSGROUP.pdf\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://flightservicebureau.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/ICAO-Doc4444-Pans-Atm-16thEdition-2016-OPSGROUP.pdf\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is by ICAO for ATS (ATC), but you can see some things mentioned in it that\u0027s relevant from pilot perspective.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT : Emergencies in Ch. 15.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-04-09T10:56:56Z\u0022 title=\u002204/09/2018 10:56  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EApril 9, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by YNM\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}